[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    353[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mAWS KMS, CloudTrail, CloudWatch.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m Same PHI infrastructure pattern as prior recipes, with elevated controls for the prediction artifacts. Customer-managed keys, CloudTrail data events on the prediction tables and the scoring API, CloudWatch alarms on calibration drift, OOD-flag rate spikes, and disagreement-alert rate spikes. Treatment recommendations are sensitive enough that the audit posture is closer to clinical-record audit than typical analytics audit.[K
